metadataAttributes.Title: Introduction to Robotic Process Automation Course
metadataAttributes.Short Intro: If you want to expand your expertise in advanced intelligent applications, then this Introduction to RPA course will put you on the fast track. RPA is one of the hottest and fastest-growing technologies for improving real-time business operations and processes. This course will give you an overview of RPA concepts, the value-add it brings with relevant business use cases and tools understanding.
